- B: [Category Shift] Building directly on the mechanism described above in the preceding analysis, This phrase suggests a different rhetorical relationship than the one required between the two clauses.
- D: [Register Clash] Blurring the sharp contrast the passage has drawn between the two claims, This phrase suggests a different rhetorical relationship than the one required between the two clauses.', NULL, 'Expression of Ideas', 'Transitions', 'reading_writing', 'expression', 'TRA', NULL, 'hard', false, 'SAT', 'multiple_choice', true, true, 'scholaris_ai', '{"rw_subtype":"transition","dsat_blueprint_v1":true,"rw_format":"transition_blank","explanation_v2":true,"generator":"regenerate-english-fresh.mjs","regen_phase2":true,"regen_agent":9,"regen_seed_offset":100000}'::jsonb, now(), now());
